text: "Mysterious" is the third and final single by Jentina from her self titled debut album, Jentina. It was released only in Italy where it reached number 49 on the Italian charts. ==Track listing== #"Mysterious" #"Mysterious" (The Vanden Plas Remix) #"Mysterious" (James Ford Remix) #"Mysterious" (Return to the Stone Age Mix) ==Chart performance== Chart (2005) Peak position Italian Singles Chart 30 ==References== Category:2005 songs Category:Jentina songs Category:Hip hop songs Category:Dance songs
